name: Saber
reason: Once the dominant stablecoin swap on Solana. Tokenomics suffered from high inflationary emissions and heavy VC unlocks, leading to significant value erosion despite functional tech.

name: Sunny Aggregator
reason: Yield aggregator that sits on top of Saber. Currently largely dormant with high risk due to lack of active development, though it retains a legacy community.

name: Port Finance
reason: A standard lending protocol from the previous cycle. Functional but struggles for market share against newer competitors. Moderate insider distribution.

name: Larix
reason: Lending protocol with a focus on RWA and metaverse assets. Face heavy competition and has seen reduced activity, increasing the risk profile.

name: Synthetify
reason: Protocol for synthetic assets. The complexity of the synthetic model and reliance on oracle integrity adds systemic risks, warranting a higher tariff.

name: Cropper
reason: Yield farming platform focused on helping new projects launch liquidity. High inflation mechanics and speculative nature of launched tokens drive the score.

name: Aldrin
reason: Comprehensive DEX with automated rebalancing tools. Good infrastructure but faces liquidity challenges compared to top-tier aggregators.

name: Media Network
reason: Decentralized Content Delivery Network (CDN). Provides actual utility and infrastructure services, separating it from pure yield farming plays.
